<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GrupoSimx - Tecnologias Emergentes</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700;900&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: { simxteal: '#0097A7', simxdark: '#1a1a2e' },
                    fontFamily: { header: ['Montserrat', 'sans-serif'], body: ['Open Sans', 'sans-serif'] }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0097A7 100%);
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.4s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 151, 167, 0.3);
        }

        .iconbox {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7 0%, #00B8D4 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.4s;
        }

        .card:hover .iconbox {
            transform: rotate(10deg) scale(1.1);
        }

        .iconbox i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .portcard {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.5s;
        }

        .portcard:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 151, 167, 0.3);
        }

        .portimg {
            height: 220px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .portimg::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 100%);
        }

        .portimg i {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4));
            transition: all 0.5s;
        }

        .portcard:hover .portimg i {
            transform: scale(1.3) rotate(8deg);
        }

        .badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 16px;
            left: 16px;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7 0%, #00B8D4 100%);
            color: white;
            font-family: Montserrat;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 50px;
            z-index: 3;
        }

        .portcard:hover .badge {
            background: white;
            color: #0097A7;
        }

        .viewbtn {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 16px;
            right: 16px;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7 0%, #00B8D4 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 3;
            transform: translateY(80px);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.4s 0.1s;
        }

        .portcard:hover .viewbtn {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .viewbtn i {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .portcontent {
            padding: 24px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .portcontent::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0097A7, #00B8D4);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.4s;
        }

        .portcard:hover .portcontent::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .portcard:hover h3 {
            color: #0097A7;
        }

        .portcard::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -3px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7, #00B8D4);
            border-radius: 27px;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s;
            filter: blur(20px);
        }

        .portcard:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .portcard::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), transparent);
            transition: left 0.6s;
            z-index: 4;
        }

        .portcard:hover::after {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .portcard {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px);
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .portcard:nth-child(1) {
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }

        .portcard:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .portcard:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        .portcard:nth-child(4) {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        .portcard:nth-child(5) {
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }

        .portcard:nth-child(6) {
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .masonry {
            column-count: 3;
            column-gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .masonry {
                column-count: 2;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .masonry {
                column-count: 1;
            }
        }

        .mbitem {
            break-inside: avoid;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .aboutcard {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.4s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .aboutcard:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 151, 167, 0.2);
        }

        .abouticon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7 0%, #00B8D4 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }

        .aboutcard:hover .abouticon {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
        }

        .abouticon i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .sectitle {
            font-family: Montserrat;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #0097A7 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .cta {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0097A7 0%, #00B8D4 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: Montserrat;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transition: all 0.4s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 151, 167, 0.4);
        }

        .cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 151, 167, 0.6);
        }

        nav {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #1a1a2e;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #0097A7;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="font-body text-slate-800 bg-white">
    <a href="login.html"
        class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 w-14 h-14 bg-simxteal hover:bg-opacity-90 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all hover:scale-110">
        <i class="fas fa-cog text-xl"></i>
    </a>
    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-simxdark/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-white/10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <img src="" alt="Logo" class="h-10">
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8">
                <a href="#hero"
                    class="text-white hover:text-simxteal transition-colors font-header uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Inicio</a>
                <a href="#about"
                    class="text-white hover:text-simxteal transition-colors font-header uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Nosotros</a>
                <a href="#services"
                    class="text-white hover:text-simxteal transition-colors font-header uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Servicios</a>
                <a href="#portfolio"
                    class="text-white hover:text-simxteal transition-colors font-header uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Portafolio</a>
                <a href="#contact"
                    class="text-white hover:text-simxteal transition-colors font-header uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Contacto</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section id="hero" class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center hero overflow-hidden">
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4">
            <img src="" alt="GrupoSimx Logo" class="h-24 mx-auto mb-6">
            <h1 class="font-header font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
                TECNOLOGIAS <span class="text-simxteal">EMERGENTES</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="font-body text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Soluciones innovadoras en automatizacion, manufactura y tecnologias emergentes para la industria
                moderna.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <a href="#services" class="cta">Nuestros Servicios</a>
                <a href="#contact"
                    class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-simxteal font-header font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-all rounded-full">Contactanos</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-white text-3xl"></i>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="sectitle mb-4">QUIENES SOMOS</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-simxteal mx-auto"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="aboutcard">
                    <div class="abouticon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye text-white text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-4 uppercase">Mision</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Brindar soluciones tecnologicas de vanguardia que transformen la
                        manera en que las empresas operan.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="aboutcard">
                    <div class="abouticon"><i class="fas fa-eye text-white text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-4 uppercase">Vision</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Ser el referente lider en tecnologias emergentes en
                        Latinoamerica.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="aboutcard">
                    <div class="abouticon"><i class="fas fa-gem text-white text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-4 uppercase">Valores</h3>
                    <ul class="font-body text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-simxteal mr-2"></i>Innovacion constante</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-simxteal mr-2"></i>Compromiso con la excelencia</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-simxteal mr-2"></i>Integridad y transparencia</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="services" class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="sectitle mb-4">NUESTROS SERVICIOS</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-simxteal mx-auto mb-4"></div>
                <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Explore nuestras soluciones especializadas.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="iconbox"><i class="fas fa-robot text-white text-2xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-3">Automatizacion</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Sistemas inteligentes para optimizar procesos industriales.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="iconbox"><i class="fas fa-cogs text-white text-2xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-3">Manufactura</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Procesos optimizados con tecnologia vanguardia.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="iconbox"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-white text-2xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-3">Drones</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Vigilancia aerial y mapeo de precision.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="iconbox"><i class="fas fa-brain text-white text-2xl"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-xl text-simxdark mb-3">Inteligencia Artificial</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Machine Learning para decisiones inteligentes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="portfolio" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="sectitle mb-4">PORTAFOLIO</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-simxteal mx-auto mb-4"></div>
                <p class="font-body text-slate-600">Conozca algunos de nuestros proyectos destacados.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="masonry">
                <div class="mbitem portcard" data-p="1">
                    <div class="portimg"><i class="fas fa-industry"></i><span class="badge">AUTOMATIZACION</span>
                        <div class="viewbtn"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="portcontent">
                        <h3 class="font-header font-bold text-lg text-simxdark">Automatizacion de Planta</h3>
                        <p class="text-sim